    <section id="main">
        <div class="container">
            <div id="mainone">

                <h2>Find Your Next Adventure !</h2>
                <p class="backgroundfortext">
                    We're here to help you dream up your next camp, figure out the details and experience at over 100+ facilities and 500+ individual sites across the country. There's something for everyone on GoCamping.com, so get out there, experience America, and bring home a story! <br />
                </p>
            </div>

